OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV union members to strike on
OL,4,Celection day ` but will STV blink?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe stakes in the STV pay dispute have
OL,7,Fjust got much higher.
OL,9,FBoth the NUJ and Bectu plan to strike
OL,10,Fin just over a fortnight on Friday 8th
OL,11,FMay.
OL,13,FThis is the day of the Scottish
OL,14,Felection results.
OL,16,FSTV is planning a special programme at
OL,17,F5pm and a peak time programme to assess
OL,18,Fthe outcome. Of course, the result is
OL,19,Falso likely to dominate its main news
OL,20,Fprogramme.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
