OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV union members to strike on
OL,4,Celection day ` but will STV blink?
OL,5,
OL,6,FYet unions are planning to target this
OL,7,Fday over a pay freeze.
OL,9,FThey must be hoping the threat of
OL,10,Fblacking out these programmes proves
OL,11,Fenough.
OL,13,FThe row over the impending end of
OL,14,FGrampian's last remnants has already
OL,15,Fdamaged the company's standing with
OL,16,Fpoliticians.
OL,18,FWhat would happen if it was unable to
OL,19,Fprovide election results coverage?
OL,21,FBut will STV blink?
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
