OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV union members to strike on
OL,4,Celection day ` but will STV blink?
OL,5,
OL,6,FLet's be brutally honest. Showing The
OL,7,FChase as usual at 5pm will probably get
OL,8,Fmore viewers and will certainly include
OL,9,Fmore advertising.
OL,11,FMost political types will probably be
OL,12,Fwatching BBC One Scotland's election
OL,13,Fcoverage which will run for most of the
OL,14,Fday.
OL,16,FSTV was already planning to show the
OL,17,Fnormal daytime schedule up to 5pm.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
