OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV union members to strike on
OL,4,Celection day ` but will STV blink?
OL,5,
OL,6,FI suspect the loss of the election
OL,7,Fcoverage would do STV huge harm amongst
OL,8,Fopinion formers and political types `
OL,9,Fthe very people already fuming vocally
OL,10,Fabout the planned news cuts.
OL,12,FBut the wider public would probably
OL,13,Ftake a more relaxed approach.
OL,15,FIt is to be hoped the strike can be
OL,16,Favoided. STV's staff have had a
OL,17,Fterrible few months ` redundancies,
OL,18,Fcuts and now a pay freeze.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
