OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV union members to strike on
OL,4,Celection day ` but will STV blink?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere is no word on whether action by
OL,7,FBectu could have a wider effect on the
OL,8,Fchannel. Will playout be affected?
OL,9,FMight disaster recovery arrangements
OL,10,Fkick in?
OL,12,FThis is a big gamble by the NUJ. Either
OL,13,FSTV will compromise or it will show
OL,14,Fwhether it can get away with a failure
OL,15,Fto cover something as vital as the
OL,16,Felection results.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
